title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 07)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

A verse I ran across earlier this morning, that spoke to my heart -- "If I must boast, I will boast of the things that show my weakness." 2 Corinthians 11:30

HIP-HOP/RAP: Anagen, Cash Hollistah, Davis Absolute, Deraj, Humble Tip, Izik Aga, Jay Carlisle, Jay Martyr, Jay Rob, Josh G Massey, Julien, KB, New 11, New Skool Spirit, New Vision, Rapture Ruckus, Street Hymns.  GOSPEL: Anthony Solin.  ROCK: Awaken The Bride, Embers In Ashes.  BLUEGRASS: Blue Highway.  POP: Bryan Popin, Radio Roman, Triple D.  CONTEMPORARY: Casey Hensley, Jason Bare, The Royal Royal.  FOLK: Charlie Parr.  HARDCORE/METAL: Colossus, Demon Hunter, Memphis May Fire, Revivalist.  ALTERNATIVE: Eliseo Way, The Gentle Wolves, John Mark McMillan, Mike Mains And The Branches, Needtobreathe.  R&B/SOUL: Erica Diamonds.  PRAISE & WORSHIP: For A Season, Johns Creek Church House, Lex Anderson, Lydell Washington, Micah Massey, Rend Collective Experiment.  SINGER-SONGWRITER: Jacob Montague, Jake Stemo.  INDIE: The Praise Record.  FOLK: SongsByDylan.  SOUNDTRACK: Various.

Our year-to-date count is up to 275 releases for 2014.
